reviewText: Great piece of U.S. History!  Every U.S. Citizen should view/watch this DVD!  Proud to buy it and proud to own it!!!
THIS WAS EXCELLENT DVD FOR ME AND MY HISTORY ALL WAS GOOD DELIVERY ALL ROUND ALL WAS EXCELLENT I REALLY ENJOY THIS KIND OF STUFF

this is a great book which gives you an overview of the smithsonian natural history museum. great introduction to what this museum has to offer. i have shared this with friends who have enjoyed it too.
